Stroop-match-RR: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incm-RR) minus meanRT(conm-RR)
Stroop-nonmatch-RR: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incnm-RR) minus meanRT(connm-RR)
Stroop-match-RS: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incm-RS) minus meanRT(conm-RS)
Stroop-nonmatch-RS: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incnm-RS) minus meanRT(connm-RS)
Stroop-match: mean diff RT(msec) =  (Stroop-match-RR + Stroop-match-RS)/2
Stroop-nonmatch: mean diff RT(msec) =  (Stroop-nonmatch-RR + Stroop-nonmatch-RS)/2
Stroop-RR: mean diff RT(msec) =  (Stroop-match-RR + Stroop-nonmatch-RR)/2
Stroop-RS: mean diff RT(msec) =  (Stroop-match-RS + Stroop-nonmatch-RS)/2
Z-score for Stroop-match-RR: difference Z-score = Z(incm-RR) minus Z(conm-RR)
Z-score for Stroop-nonmatch-RR: difference Z-score = Z(incnm-RR) minus Z(connm-RR)
Z-score for Stroop-match-RS: difference Z-score = Z(incm-RS) minus Z(conm-RS)
Z-score for Stroop-nonmatch-RS: difference Z-score = Z(incnm-RS) minus Z(connm-RS)
Z-score for Stroop-match: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-match-RR + Z-score Stroop-match-RS)/2
Z-score for Stroop-nonmatch: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RR + Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RS)/2
Z-score for Stroop-RR: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-match-RR + Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RR)/2
Z-score for Stroop-RS: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-match-RS + Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RS)/2
